<div id="attachment_246804" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246804" class="wp-image-246804 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-10.jpg" alt="a miniature knit cardigan inspired by Picasso" width="1920" height="1760" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-10.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-10-640x587.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-10-960x880.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-10-1536x1408.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
