</div>
<div id="attachment_246807" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246807" class="wp-image-246807 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-14.jpg" alt="three miniature knit sweaters worn on three fingers to show scale" width="1920" height="1628" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-14.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-14-640x543.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-14-960x814.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/crome-14-1536x1302.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246807" class="wp-caption-text">“Sheep Farm” series</p>
</div>
