<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246758 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/type-7.jpg" alt="a blue and white knit square with text" width="1920" height="1631" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/type-7.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/type-7-640x544.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/type-7-960x816.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/type-7-1536x1305.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
